<br>
Have a story of a single begger. He sees me first in a dungeon and offers me all of his paladin quest armor for Shieldstorm, which I had just bought and was testing, was my only 2hs and I am not rich. I felt sorry for him and answered that his BP and a couple items were easily worth the money for a ss and that I bought this more for raids where I could use the extra saves. Told him he should sell a couple pieces and get himself an Arbitors combine if he wanted a decent 2hs. I gave him a couple items I had just to be cool.<br>
<br>
Next Time I see him he says &quot;Give me that Sword!&quot; and starts gettin pushy and repeatedly demanding that I loan it to him.<br>
Whatcha gonna do with these guys?<br>
